# --- No client data in this platform repo (see docs/CONVENTIONS in README §Provenance) ---
# App-level artefacts, seed CSVs with real identifiers, or client demo apps do NOT belong here.

# Delivery renders (DOCX/PDF) are published as GitHub Release assets, not committed
docs/*.docx
docs/*.pdf
